368
00:19:20,839 --> 00:19:22,960
Compare them with the database.

369
00:19:23,920 --> 00:19:25,279
See if there's any criminal record.

370
00:19:26,720 --> 00:19:30,319
Send a notice to the hospitals as well.

371
00:19:30,799 --> 00:19:32,279
Check if anyone has sought medical treatment.

372
00:19:33,359 --> 00:19:34,720
His head was split open.

373
00:19:36,039 --> 00:19:38,079
Normally, he wouldn't be able to handle it himself.

374
00:19:40,880 --> 00:19:44,200
Get the sketch artist here as soon as possible.

375
00:19:44,759 --> 00:19:46,799
See if, based on everyone's descriptions,

376
00:19:47,200 --> 00:19:49,240
he can draw a rough sketch.

377
00:19:50,200 --> 00:19:50,720
Yes.

378
00:19:50,720 --> 00:19:51,440
Also,

379
00:19:54,599 --> 00:19:55,480
stay in close contact with headquarters.

380
00:19:56,880 --> 00:19:58,319
Maintain close communication.

381
00:19:58,319 --> 00:19:59,720
If there's any new information,

382
00:20:00,519 --> 00:20:01,319
report it immediately.

383
00:20:01,319 --> 00:20:02,039
Understood.

384
00:20:02,359 --> 00:20:03,039
Captain Huang,

385
00:20:04,480 --> 00:20:05,519
