393
00:20:20,559 --> 00:20:22,240
We need to check both the traffic police and the bus stop.

394
00:20:22,519 --> 00:20:23,440
I'll go to the traffic police.

395
00:20:23,599 --> 00:20:24,440
The two of us will go to the bus stop.

396
00:20:31,839 --> 00:20:33,559
Guess how much money was in that wallet.

397
00:20:34,160 --> 00:20:34,799
How much?

398
00:20:35,680 --> 00:20:36,839
Forty-seven yuan and sixty cents.

399
00:20:38,240 --> 00:20:39,680
All for forty-seven yuan and sixty cents.

400
00:20:40,440 --> 00:20:41,720
They stabbed Old Ma to death.

401
00:20:58,240 --> 00:20:59,640
Old Ma died unjustly.

402
00:21:01,920 --> 00:21:03,200
Follow the direction of the blood trail.

403
00:21:03,640 --> 00:21:05,720
At the bus stop two kilometers from the crime scene

404
00:21:06,119 --> 00:21:06,720
it stopped.

405
00:21:15,720 --> 00:21:16,960
I'm not going to the morning market area.

406
00:21:16,960 --> 00:21:18,359
If you don't go, who will?

407
00:21:18,640 --> 00:21:21,400
A while ago, a few thieves showed up around here.

408
00:21:21,759 --> 00:21:22,880
Do you know who did it?

409
00:21:22,880 --> 00:21:23,680
Who?

410
00:21:24,720 --> 00:21:25,559
Just these few people.

411
00:21:31,440 --> 00:21:32,960
Probably a lot of people have seen him.

412
00:21:38,839 --> 00:21:39,400
That's him.

413
00:21:45,200 --> 00:21:45,880
May I ask you something?

414
00:21:46,200 --> 00:21:47,039
Have you seen this person?

415
00:21:47,039 --> 00:21:48,039
Really haven't seen him.

416
00:21:48,200 --> 00:21:49,759
Excuse me, have you seen this person?

417
00:21:49,880 --> 00:21:50,519
No, no.

418
00:21:51,519 --> 00:21:53,839
Hello, could you please take a look and see if you've seen this person?

419
00:21:54,119 --> 00:21:54,640
Hello.

420
00:21:54,640 --> 00:21:55,599
Please show your ID and driver's license.

421
00:21:55,920 --> 00:21:56,960
I don't think I've seen him.

422
00:21:57,079 --> 00:21:57,799
Tall and thin.

423
00:21:57,799 --> 00:21:58,920
Looks quite energetic.

424
00:21:59,559 --> 00:22:00,279
Haven't seen him.

425
00:22:00,359 --> 00:22:01,000
Thank you.

426
00:22:01,640 --> 00:22:02,480
Haven't seen him.

427
00:22:04,599 --> 00:22:05,200
I've seen him.

428
00:22:05,400 --> 00:22:06,559
He came alone.

429
00:22:06,799 --> 00:22:07,640
When did he come?

430
00:22:07,640 --> 00:22:10,119
He got into a fight and hurt his head.

431
00:22:10,119 --> 00:22:12,440
I gave him emergency treatment and bandaged it up.

432
00:22:12,440 --> 00:22:13,559
You bandaged him?

433
00:22:13,599 --> 00:22:15,720
This is a barbershop—do you even know how to bandage wounds?

434
00:22:16,160 --> 00:22:17,720
I was worried he might get tetanus.

435
00:22:18,359 --> 00:22:20,119
I just wanted to do a good deed, so I bandaged him.

436
00:22:20,119 --> 00:22:21,440
Why did he come here?

437
00:22:21,640 --> 00:22:22,559
Do you know each other?

438
00:22:22,559 --> 00:22:23,319
No, I don't.

439
00:22:23,319 --> 00:22:24,759
You don't know him, so why did you help him?

440
00:22:24,759 --> 00:22:26,440
He paid me a lot.

441
00:22:26,880 --> 00:22:28,440
So you helped him just because he paid you more?

442
00:22:29,279 --> 00:22:30,640
Be careful next time, be careful.

443
00:22:31,480 --> 00:22:32,640
Did the bandaging leave anything behind?

444
00:22:33,880 --> 00:22:36,160
Here, look, it's all contaminated.

445
00:22:40,240 --> 00:22:41,160
How did he leave?

446
00:22:41,359 --> 00:22:42,960
He left alone, riding a bicycle.

447
00:22:43,160 --> 00:22:44,000
Where does he live?

448
00:22:44,160 --> 00:22:45,559
I really don't know about that.

449
00:22:45,599 --> 00:22:46,440
Where did he go?

450
00:22:46,799 --> 00:22:48,000
I don't know that either.

451
00:22:49,799 --> 00:22:51,000
He dared to bandage himself here.

452
00:22:51,000 --> 00:22:52,559
That means this area is his safe zone.

453
00:22:52,559 --> 00:22:53,720
He must live nearby.

454
00:22:54,559 --> 00:22:55,720
Sooner or later, he'll have to go out.

455
00:22:56,160 --> 00:22:57,160
I'll go call for backup.

456
00:22:57,240 --> 00:22:58,279
Use this shop as the center.

457
00:22:58,480 --> 00:22:59,799
Mark out the area and visit each house.

458
00:23:01,599 --> 00:23:02,799
Sir, do you recognize this person?

459
00:23:02,799 --> 00:23:03,480
Haven't seen him.

460
00:23:03,559 --> 00:23:04,240
No, I haven't.

461
00:23:04,400 --> 00:23:04,960
Thank you.

462
00:23:07,559 --> 00:23:08,960
Thank you, thank you.

463
00:23:09,000 --> 00:23:10,279
It's nothing, thank you.

464
00:23:10,480 --> 00:23:12,079
Sir, do you know this person?

465
00:23:13,799 --> 00:23:16,000
Hello, have you seen this person?

466
00:23:16,559 --> 00:23:17,079
No, I haven't.

467
00:23:17,559 --> 00:23:19,720
Please take another look, he looks quite sharp.

468
00:23:19,720 --> 00:23:21,480
Hello, have you seen this person?

469
00:23:25,359 --> 00:23:26,960
Hello, have you seen this person?

470
00:23:29,640 --> 00:23:30,720
Please take a good look.

471
00:23:31,440 --> 00:23:31,880
Ziming.

472
00:23:31,960 --> 00:23:32,799
What's wrong? It's nothing.

473
00:23:33,240 --> 00:23:33,680
Brother Lei.

474
00:23:34,519 --> 00:23:35,079
Master.

475
00:23:37,680 --> 00:23:39,359
Doctor, how is he?

476
00:23:39,400 --> 00:23:40,519
Acute gastric ulcer.

477
00:23:40,559 --> 00:23:42,519
If you had come any later, it might have perforated.

478
00:23:42,960 --> 00:23:44,720
His eating habits must be really irregular.

479
00:23:44,839 --> 00:23:45,640
Is it serious?

480
00:23:45,720 --> 00:23:48,079
He must be hospitalized for IV treatment and cooperate with us.

481
00:23:48,720 --> 00:23:49,640
He needs to rest for a while.

482
00:23:49,680 --> 00:23:51,279
Otherwise, his health will really collapse.

483
00:23:52,279 --> 00:23:53,319
Go handle the admission procedures.

484
00:23:53,440 --> 00:23:54,319
Thank you, doctor.

485
00:23:54,920 --> 00:23:56,000
Thank you, you've worked hard.

486
00:24:02,000 --> 00:24:03,440
Hello, hello.

487
00:24:03,440 --> 00:24:04,759
Please take a look. Have you seen this person before?

488
00:24:04,759 --> 00:24:05,440
I don't know.

489
00:24:05,519 --> 00:24:06,240
Hello.

490
00:24:06,519 --> 00:24:08,079
Please take a look. Have you seen this person before?

491
00:24:08,079 --> 00:24:09,160
I haven't seen him.

492
00:24:09,359 --> 00:24:09,880
I have.

493
00:24:11,039 --> 00:24:12,680
He came here this morning to eat steamed buns.

494
00:24:14,039 --> 00:24:15,480
Did he have gauze wrapped around his head?

495
00:24:15,480 --> 00:24:16,240
Yes.

496
00:24:16,240 --> 00:24:18,720
He also had white gauze wrapped around, and there was blood.

497
00:24:18,920 --> 00:24:19,799
This morning?

498
00:24:20,200 --> 00:24:20,880
Around five or six o'clock.

499
00:24:21,799 --> 00:24:22,960
When he was eating here,

500
00:24:22,960 --> 00:24:23,960
did he say anything?

501
00:24:23,960 --> 00:24:24,640
He didn't say much.

502
00:24:24,839 --> 00:24:25,920
What could he say while just eating?

503
00:24:26,079 --> 00:24:27,160
Think carefully.

504
00:24:28,000 --> 00:24:29,039
Did he make a phone call?

505
00:24:29,599 --> 00:24:30,359
He did.

506
00:24:30,559 --> 00:24:32,119
He seemed to say he was going back to his hometown.

507
00:24:33,559 --> 00:24:34,839
Do you know where he lives?

508
00:24:35,200 --> 00:24:37,400
I think I saw him coming out from the entrance of this alley.

509
00:24:37,880 --> 00:24:38,759
He walked out from there.

510
00:24:41,039 --> 00:24:42,079
Alright, thank you.

511
00:24:43,160 --> 00:24:44,359
