514
00:24:47,160 --> 00:24:48,559
He ordered a basket of pork and cabbage buns.

515
00:24:49,559 --> 00:24:50,480
Okay, thank you.

516
00:24:53,440 --> 00:24:54,599
Why are you asking about the bun filling?

517
00:24:54,920 --> 00:24:55,720
My mentor once said,

518
00:24:56,559 --> 00:24:57,920
if the suspect commits suicide

519
00:24:58,279 --> 00:24:59,960
