521
00:25:03,480 --> 00:25:04,279
What should we do?

522
00:25:04,680 --> 00:25:05,480
We wait and watch.

523
00:25:05,960 --> 00:25:06,920
The two of us don't have enough manpower.

524
00:25:06,920 --> 00:25:07,880
I'll notify Captain Huang.

525
00:25:32,200 --> 00:25:33,640
Da Liu, Chaozi

526
00:25:33,799 --> 00:25:34,640
Keep a close watch for me.

527
00:25:34,759 --> 00:25:35,799
Don't doze off.

528
00:25:36,440 --> 00:25:37,200
Got it.

529
00:25:49,359 --> 00:25:50,160
Where are you going?

530
00:25:50,599 --> 00:25:51,519
I'm going to check it out.

531
00:25:52,119 --> 00:25:53,319
Wait for him to come out.

532
00:25:53,759 --> 00:25:55,000
