538
00:26:21,039 --> 00:26:22,480
Target spotted. Target spotted.

539
00:26:29,880 --> 00:26:31,440
It's ready, get prepared.

540
00:26:41,359 --> 00:26:42,839
Don't move! Don't move! Don't move!

541
00:26:45,319 --> 00:26:46,160
What are you doing?

542
00:26:46,160 --> 00:26:46,799
What's your name? Don't move!

543
00:26:46,799 --> 00:26:47,680
What are you doing?

544
00:26:47,880 --> 00:26:48,640
Speak! What's your name?

545
00:26:50,039 --> 00:26:50,559
A knife!

546
00:26:50,880 --> 00:26:51,400
Pull him up!

547
00:26:51,400 --> 00:26:52,720
Get up! Get up! Get up!

548
00:26:58,079 --> 00:26:58,920
Are you Zhou Xiaocheng?

549
00:26:59,359 --> 00:27:00,400
You've got the wrong person.

550
00:27:02,359 --> 00:27:03,000
Team, fall back.

551
00:27:03,880 --> 00:27:04,759
Take him away. Move.

552
00:27:08,200 --> 00:27:09,000
What's your name?

553
00:27:09,799 --> 00:27:10,599
Zhou Xiaocheng.

554
00:27:11,119 --> 00:27:11,920
Age?

555
00:27:12,200 --> 00:27:13,079
Nineteen.

556
00:27:13,079 --> 00:27:13,839
Place of origin?

557
00:27:14,599 --> 00:27:15,400
Mengcheng.

558
00:27:16,640 --> 00:27:17,759
Why did you steal?

559
00:27:18,720 --> 00:27:20,039
I've been here for over half a year.

560
00:27:20,559 --> 00:27:22,079
It was hard to find a job.

