I worked as an apprentice in the kitchen.

562
00:27:24,799 --> 00:27:26,200
But the boss ran away unexpectedly.

563
00:27:26,839 --> 00:27:27,960
The restaurant was shut down.

564
00:27:28,519 --> 00:27:31,640
I... I really ran out of money.

565
00:27:31,799 --> 00:27:33,640
If you had no money, why were you carrying a knife?

566
00:27:34,680 --> 00:27:36,000
Were you ready to stab someone at any time?

567
00:27:36,000 --> 00:27:37,160
I didn't mean to stab him.

568
00:27:37,160 --> 00:27:38,039
I just wanted to run.

569
00:27:40,200 --> 00:27:41,359
Boss, how much is this?

570
00:27:41,480 --> 00:27:42,079
Four yuan.

571
00:27:43,160 --> 00:27:44,880
Boss, how much is this cabbage?

572
00:27:44,880 --> 00:27:45,440
What are you doing?

573
00:27:45,799 --> 00:27:46,279
What?

574
00:27:46,279 --> 00:27:47,119
Whose stuff is this?

575
00:27:47,319 --> 00:27:48,160
It's mine.

576
00:27:48,359 --> 00:27:48,839
Don't move.

577
00:27:48,839 --> 00:27:49,559
I didn't steal it.

578
00:27:49,720 --> 00:27:50,200
That's my wallet.

579
00:27:50,200 --> 00:27:51,599
Come with me to the police station to make a statement.

580
00:27:52,559 --> 00:27:55,240
I thought I saw a police badge on him.

581
00:27:55,920 --> 00:27:56,960
I got scared.

582
00:27:57,440 --> 00:27:59,039
Let's go, to the police station.

583
00:28:01,240 --> 00:28:02,279
Catch the thief

584
00:28:03,079 --> 00:28:04,240
I stabbed him

585
00:28:11,359 --> 00:28:11,839
Hello

586
00:28:27,079 --> 00:28:27,640
Understood.

587
00:28:32,079 --> 00:28:33,119
Everyone, take a look.

588
00:28:33,480 --> 00:28:34,799
This is from 1983,

589
00:28:34,799 --> 00:28:36,519
a tragic case that happened in Mengcheng.

590
00:28:37,039 --> 00:28:39,039
The couple ran a leather goods business.

591
00:28:39,039 --> 00:28:41,000
They were found hacked to death in their home.

592
00:28:41,000 --> 00:28:41,759
What's more important is,

593
00:28:41,759 --> 00:28:44,200
their eight-year-old only son was also severely injured.

594
00:28:44,200 --> 00:28:46,440
The key issue was that, due to limited technology at the time,

595
00:28:46,799 --> 00:28:48,759
the suspect's identity could never be determined.

596
00:28:48,759 --> 00:28:50,039
So the investigation couldn't move forward.

597
00:28:50,079 --> 00:28:51,000
As you all know,

598
00:28:51,200 --> 00:28:52,960
every team has a case that haunts them.

599
00:28:53,559 --> 00:28:56,039
This case is the one that haunts their team.

600
00:28:56,160 --> 00:28:59,480
Whenever a new member joins, the first file they review

601
00:28:59,640 --> 00:29:00,920
is the one you have in your hands.

602
00:29:01,319 --> 00:29:02,920
This time, with Zhou Xiaocheng,

603
00:29:03,079 --> 00:29:03,799
the DNA

604
00:29:03,799 --> 00:29:04,759
test report just came out,

605
00:29:05,759 --> 00:29:07,640
and there has been a major breakthrough in the case.

606
00:29:07,880 --> 00:29:10,319
After a careful comparison by our forensics team,

607
00:29:10,559 --> 00:29:11,359
in Zhou Xiaocheng's

608
00:29:11,359 --> 00:29:12,880
DNA chromosomes,

609
00:29:13,160 --> 00:29:16,119
they found a match with the DNA

610
00:29:16,319 --> 00:29:17,599
extracted from the evidence of this murder case.

611
00:29:17,799 --> 00:29:19,319
There is a familial relationship.

612
00:29:19,720 --> 00:29:21,319
So Liu Yang, you and Ziming,

613
00:29:21,519 --> 00:29:23,240
hurry to Mengcheng.

614
00:29:23,519 --> 00:29:24,960
Take Zhou Xiaocheng's

615
00:29:24,960 --> 00:29:26,400
DNA sample and deliver it to them.

616
00:29:26,400 --> 00:29:27,519
Assist them with the investigation.

617
00:29:27,519 --> 00:29:28,119
Got it.

618
00:29:34,440 --> 00:29:36,839
I had just joined the police force back then.

619
00:29:38,680 --> 00:29:40,200
I remember it very clearly.

620
00:29:40,799 --> 00:29:42,400
It was September 30th that day.

621
00:29:43,279 --> 00:29:44,079
The weather was especially stuffy.

622
00:29:44,279 --> 00:29:45,680
It was so stifling, I could hardly breathe.

623
00:29:45,839 --> 00:29:46,839
In the evening,

624
00:29:47,680 --> 00:29:49,000
after days of holding back, the heavy rain

625
00:29:49,119 --> 00:29:50,319
finally poured down.

626
00:29:51,480 --> 00:29:52,240
Help!

627
00:29:52,240 --> 00:29:53,200
Usually, the child

628
00:29:53,359 --> 00:29:54,680
would have dinner at a classmate's house.

629
00:29:54,759 --> 00:29:55,519
Help!

630
00:29:55,519 --> 00:29:56,480
It was pouring that day.

631
00:29:56,480 --> 00:29:57,640
The parents came home early.

632
00:29:58,440 --> 00:30:00,279
So they picked up the child on the way.

633
00:30:00,440 --> 00:30:00,839
Help!

634
00:30:00,839 --> 00:30:02,839
The child was walking behind them with an umbrella.

635
00:30:03,279 --> 00:30:05,839
As soon as they entered the yard, the child found the parents had been slashed.

636
00:30:06,440 --> 00:30:09,200
Terrified, the child turned and ran away, shouting.

637
00:30:09,200 --> 00:30:10,839
But was caught at the gate.

638
00:30:10,839 --> 00:30:11,799
And was stabbed several times.

639
00:30:13,079 --> 00:30:14,359
The two attackers ran away.

640
00:30:15,000 --> 00:30:17,119
Luckily, a neighbor rushed the child to the hospital in time.

641
00:30:17,119 --> 00:30:18,039
There's been a murder!

642
00:30:18,039 --> 00:30:19,319
That's how the child barely survived. There's been a murder!

643
00:30:19,559 --> 00:30:20,279
There's been a murder.

644
00:30:20,880 --> 00:30:21,200
There's been a murder.

645
00:30:21,200 --> 00:30:23,359
Was it revenge or for money?

646
00:30:24,079 --> 00:30:25,000
I don't know.

647
00:30:25,200 --> 00:30:26,240
The child is too young.

648
00:30:26,440 --> 00:30:27,440
Can't explain clearly.

649
00:30:28,319 --> 00:30:30,359
Based on the child's and neighbors' descriptions,

650
00:30:30,440 --> 00:30:32,400
and the footprints in the room,

651
00:30:32,839 --> 00:30:34,440
there were probably two perpetrators.

652
00:30:34,599 --> 00:30:36,000
But where did they come from?

653
00:30:36,279 --> 00:30:37,319
Where did they go?

654
00:30:37,480 --> 00:30:38,559
And why did they do it?

655
00:30:38,680 --> 00:30:39,960
We have no clues at all.

656
00:30:40,799 --> 00:30:44,440
Back then, we only had fingerprint collection technology.

657
00:30:44,960 --> 00:30:47,160
But that required manual comparison, one by one.

658
00:30:48,000 --> 00:30:48,920
The efficiency was...

659
00:30:49,440 --> 00:30:52,079
Was that blood sample from the scene?

660
00:30:52,079 --> 00:30:52,759
Yes.

661
00:30:53,200 --> 00:30:54,039
Just one drop.

662
00:30:54,359 --> 00:30:55,640
A drip stain.

663
00:30:56,720 --> 00:30:57,640
At the doorway.

664
00:30:57,920 --> 00:30:59,720
It just happened to avoid the rain.

665
00:31:00,519 --> 00:31:01,839
Just this one drop of blood.

666
00:31:02,599 --> 00:31:04,599
Its blood type was different from all the victims.

667
00:31:05,759 --> 00:31:06,720
But at that time, there was no

668
00:31:06,720 --> 00:31:07,839
DNA technology.

669
00:31:10,640 --> 00:31:12,079
So what's the situation now?

670
00:31:12,720 --> 00:31:14,160
We've already taken

671
00:31:14,160 --> 00:31:15,839
blood samples from three of Zhou Xiaocheng's male immediate relatives

672
00:31:16,279 --> 00:31:17,759
for testing.

673
00:31:19,359 --> 00:31:20,319
The comparison is underway.

674
00:31:20,440 --> 00:31:22,200
We could have the results as early as tomorrow morning.

675
00:31:37,039 --> 00:31:37,920
Come have some water. Thank you.

676
00:31:37,920 --> 00:31:38,400
I just made it.

677
00:31:38,400 --> 00:31:39,039
Thank you.

678
00:31:45,119 --> 00:31:45,759
Hello

679
00:31:49,200 --> 00:31:50,200
Master, I've found out the truth.

680
00:31:50,200 --> 00:31:51,920
It's Zhou Xiaocheng's father, Zhou Bingsheng.

681
00:31:53,160 --> 00:31:53,599
Let's go.

682
00:31:54,079 --> 00:31:54,599
Master

683
00:31:54,599 --> 00:31:56,240
Your back hasn't fully recovered yet, you shouldn't go.

684
00:31:56,240 --> 00:31:57,759
Are you kidding? Let's go.

685
00:32:23,480 --> 00:32:24,079
Where are you going?

686
00:32:24,559 --> 00:32:25,640
Stop! Don't move.

687
00:32:30,960 --> 00:32:31,440
Don't move.

688
00:32:32,200 --> 00:32:32,640
Hands.

689
00:32:33,440 --> 00:32:33,920
That's him.

690
00:32:33,920 --> 00:32:34,599
What's your name?

691
00:32:34,960 --> 00:32:35,880
Zhou Bingsheng.

692
00:32:36,039 --> 00:32:37,240
Do you know why we're looking for you?

693
00:32:40,880 --> 00:32:41,599
I know.

694
00:32:43,759 --> 00:32:44,880
For murder.

695
00:32:45,079 --> 00:32:46,079
When did you kill?

696
00:32:49,240 --> 00:32:50,160
In 1983.

697
00:32:51,480 --> 00:32:52,079
Let's go.

698
00:32:57,000 --> 00:32:57,720
Speak.

699
00:32:58,440 --> 00:32:59,400
Why did you kill?

700
00:33:00,160 --> 00:33:00,880
For money.

701
00:33:01,480 --> 00:33:03,240
If it was for money, why didn't you just rob someone?

702
00:33:04,200 --> 00:33:07,599
Back then, I was supposed to take over my father's job.

703
00:33:08,920 --> 00:33:10,599
I was supposed to work at the factory.

704
00:33:11,759 --> 00:33:14,160
But someone else took my spot.

705
00:33:15,359 --> 00:33:18,279
I felt wronged and frustrated.

706
00:33:19,240 --> 00:33:20,559
So I started gambling.

707
00:33:22,759 --> 00:33:24,960
I had bad luck and lost all my money.

708
00:33:25,519 --> 00:33:26,559
I had no other options.

709
00:33:30,440 --> 00:33:32,640
What was your relationship with the two victims?

710
00:33:33,440 --> 00:33:34,400
No relationship.

711
00:33:36,119 --> 00:33:37,839
They just used my car twice.

712
00:33:38,359 --> 00:33:39,279
For prostitution.

713
00:33:41,440 --> 00:33:42,960
Why did you target them?

714
00:33:43,839 --> 00:33:44,720
Because they had money.

715
00:33:45,920 --> 00:33:46,720
Go on.

716
00:33:47,839 --> 00:33:50,160
There was another person involved. Who was it?

717
00:33:51,319 --> 00:33:53,559
My fellow townsman, Fei Yong.

718
00:33:54,359 --> 00:33:55,359
How did you meet?

719
00:33:56,000 --> 00:33:57,200
We met playing cards.

720
00:33:57,200 --> 00:33:57,880
Where is he?

721
00:33:59,119 --> 00:34:01,599
He died of cancer two years ago.

722
00:34:02,759 --> 00:34:05,319
Have you been in contact with your son Zhou Xiaocheng recently?

723
00:34:06,720 --> 00:34:07,720
No contact.

724
00:34:08,639 --> 00:34:09,960
He's studying out of town.

725
00:34:12,039 --> 00:34:13,280
Don't tell him about this.

726
00:34:14,239 --> 00:34:15,800
Don't let it interfere with his studies.

727
00:34:16,920 --> 00:34:18,960
The other suspect, Fei Yong, has already been identified.

728
00:34:19,760 --> 00:34:21,679
He did pass away from lung cancer the year before last.

729
00:34:21,920 --> 00:34:23,159
But this time, it's all thanks to you.

730
00:34:23,239 --> 00:34:24,800
If we hadn't caught Zhou Xiaocheng,

731
00:34:25,000 --> 00:34:26,920
who knows when this case would have been solved.

732
00:34:27,239 --> 00:34:28,119
Don't mention it.

733
00:34:28,119 --> 00:34:29,519
We didn't really do much to help.

734
00:34:29,840 --> 00:34:31,280
The blood samples you kept from the suspects

735
00:34:31,280 --> 00:34:32,360
were the key to solving the case.

736
00:34:33,679 --> 00:34:34,679
Now that this case is closed,

737
00:34:34,679 --> 00:34:36,960
my mentor can finally let go of this burden.

738
00:34:39,400 --> 00:34:40,280
Uncle Tao,

739
00:34:41,400 --> 00:34:42,360
you're getting on in years too.

740
00:34:42,360 --> 00:34:43,960
I guess you're the victim's child. Take care of yourself.

741
00:34:45,159 --> 00:34:47,639
Me too, I'm especially grateful to you.

742
00:34:47,639 --> 00:34:49,000
We finally caught them.

743
00:34:51,039 --> 00:34:52,119
But honestly, I wish even more

744
00:34:52,119 --> 00:34:53,719
they had never come to my home,

745
00:34:54,159 --> 00:34:55,320
and never killed my parents.

746
00:35:47,360 --> 00:35:48,159
Moment of silence

747
00:35:57,760 --> 00:35:58,880
Moment of silence is over.

748
00:36:01,960 --> 00:36:02,880
First bow

749
00:36:08,280 --> 00:36:09,280
Second bow

750
00:36:14,679 --> 00:36:15,559
Three bows

751
00:36:20,000 --> 00:36:21,079
Salute

752
00:36:49,679 --> 00:36:50,519
You're back.

753
00:36:54,079 --> 00:36:57,079
Didn't I say I wanted beige walls?

754
00:36:57,480 --> 00:36:58,920
What color is this?

755
00:37:00,440 --> 00:37:02,119
This is way too different.

756
00:37:08,239 --> 00:37:09,079
I'm sorry.

757
00:37:11,440 --> 00:37:12,559
I bought the wrong one.

758
00:37:17,800 --> 00:37:18,800
What's wrong?

759
00:37:19,760 --> 00:37:22,519
It's nothing, it's nothing. This color looks nice too.

760
00:37:40,039 --> 00:37:40,800
Tingting

761
00:37:45,360 --> 00:37:46,639
Let's break up.

762
00:37:49,559 --> 00:37:50,360
No, we won't.

763
00:37:52,519 --> 00:37:53,800
I know what you're afraid of.

764
00:37:55,159 --> 00:37:56,760
Then I won't break up with you either.

765
00:37:57,239 --> 00:37:58,599
Liu Ziming, remember this.

766
00:37:58,760 --> 00:38:01,159
You will belong to me, Fang Tingting, for your whole life.

767
00:38:01,599 --> 00:38:02,760
Even if you die,

768
00:38:03,599 --> 00:38:04,960
you'll still be mine, Fang Tingting's.

769
00:39:08,440 --> 00:39:09,440
Wait a moment.

770
00:39:11,360 --> 00:39:12,920
I heard you're getting your marriage certificate.

771
00:39:14,280 --> 00:39:15,719
You probably won't come back after that, right?

772
00:39:16,000 --> 00:39:16,679
Yes.

773
00:39:18,280 --> 00:39:18,760
Come.

774
00:39:20,599 --> 00:39:21,840
Take a look at how it's written.

775
00:39:22,360 --> 00:39:23,159
Do you know them?

776
00:39:23,880 --> 00:39:25,880
Your calligraphy is really good.

777
00:39:25,920 --> 00:39:27,320
I'll have it framed later.

778
00:39:27,880 --> 00:39:30,079
I'll give it to you as a wedding gift.

779
00:39:30,320 --> 00:39:31,519
I appreciate your kindness.

780
00:39:31,679 --> 00:39:32,920
You should keep it for yourself.

781
00:39:32,920 --> 00:39:34,719
Frame it and hang it by your bedside.

782
00:39:35,360 --> 00:39:36,800
Here's your key back.

783
00:39:50,480 --> 00:39:51,920
This is way too far.

784
00:39:52,440 --> 00:39:53,960
Mom, you just don't get it.

785
00:39:54,280 --> 00:39:55,960
