789
00:40:01,199 --> 00:40:02,480
It's definitely real.

790
00:40:03,039 --> 00:40:05,840
I went there last time for a case.

791
00:40:05,960 --> 00:40:07,039
There are dozens of pools.

792
00:40:07,079 --> 00:40:08,519
All kinds, big and small.

793
00:40:09,840 --> 00:40:10,679
They even have fish therapy.

794
00:40:11,119 --> 00:40:11,920
Fish therapy?

795
00:40:12,480 --> 00:40:13,679
It's a kind of small fish.

796
00:40:14,239 --> 00:40:16,280
They live specifically in hot springs.

797
00:40:16,719 --> 00:40:19,320
They swim around and nibble on your feet.

798
00:40:19,320 --> 00:40:21,719
They say they eat the dead skin on your feet.

799
00:40:22,719 --> 00:40:24,280
That sounds gross.

800
00:40:24,400 --> 00:40:25,679
It's not gross, it's actually really fun.

801
00:40:25,679 --> 00:40:27,039
You'll know once you try it.

802
00:40:27,280 --> 00:40:28,239
I can give it a try.

803
00:40:28,239 --> 00:40:30,280
Just don't leave me halfway through soaking and trying it.

804
00:40:30,280 --> 00:40:31,920
And then you leave.

805
00:40:32,119 --> 00:40:34,280
Yeah, you leave halfway.

806
00:40:34,280 --> 00:40:35,960
What if the little fish don't get enough to eat?

807
00:40:36,639 --> 00:40:37,559
That's impossible.

808
00:40:37,840 --> 00:40:39,519
I took three days off from the team.

809
00:40:39,760 --> 00:40:41,320
We'll soak for three days.

810
00:40:41,360 --> 00:40:43,039
Try out every single pool.

811
00:40:43,559 --> 00:40:45,239
Won't our skin be all peeled off by then?

812
00:40:45,679 --> 00:40:46,480
Three days?

813
00:40:46,719 --> 00:40:48,559
Won't all that dead skin make the fish burst?

814
00:40:56,280 --> 00:40:57,280
Don't answer it.

815
00:40:58,960 --> 00:41:00,320
Let me see what it's about.

816
00:41:02,400 --> 00:41:03,000
Hello?

817
00:41:05,039 --> 00:41:06,599
