824
00:41:40,480 --> 00:41:42,159
And that's with you being the closest one.

825
00:41:42,880 --> 00:41:44,559
They can't even get a cab over there.

826
00:41:45,159 --> 00:41:46,960
I'll treat you to a meal later, okay?

827
00:41:48,119 --> 00:41:49,239
Alright, two meals.

828
00:41:49,800 --> 00:41:50,679
You pick the place.

829
00:41:51,320 --> 00:41:51,960
Alright, alright.

830
00:41:51,960 --> 00:41:53,519
Hurry up and get going.

831
00:41:55,039 --> 00:41:56,000
I'll cover the gas.

832
00:41:56,719 --> 00:41:58,760
But whatever you do, don't run any red lights.

833
00:41:59,400 --> 00:42:00,679
Enough, stop talking nonsense.

834
00:42:00,679 --> 00:42:02,280
Bro, just get over there quickly.

835
00:42:02,599 --> 00:42:03,760
The weather forecast says it's going to rain soon.

836
00:42:03,760 --> 00:42:04,920
And they're not dressed warmly.

837
00:42:06,199 --> 00:42:07,920
